title: Patti Smith 1971-12-25 Poetry Project, St Mark's Church, NYC
description:
Patti Smith
December 25, 1971
The Poetry Project, St. Marks Church, New York City, USA

Until 10 February 1971 was released this was the earliest Patti recording I'd seen.

Lineage: FM SBD recording of otherwise unknown lineage--CDR I received by mail--EAC--Sound Forge--FLAC(level 8)

SQ:  Not good, I rate it "C-".  Downloaded about six hundred times on Demonoid.

For full NFO please view:  <a href=" http://bayimg.com/mAdMmaAef" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://bayimg.com/mAdMmaAef</a>    
    (because PirateBay has a length limit for torrent Descriptions)

In the full NFO you will see mention of an alternate, inferior source.  See a comparison at  <a href=" http://bayimg.com/paDlDAaEf" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://bayimg.com/paDlDAaEf</a>   (this source is on the bottom, the inferior Dime source is on the top; spectrals of the whole recording, and two seconds of it, are on the left and middle, with peaks on the right)

Spectral view and frequency analysis of this torrent at  <a href=" http://bayimg.com/padlEaAEf" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://bayimg.com/padlEaAEf</a>
